parameters: (There's a long sword inside the drawer)

(I can feel a strong power emanating from this
sword...)\F[4]

"O white deity. I am grateful for the release of
the sealed sword. With the demon-breaking power of
the sword, I have been able to escape the bonds of
the calamitous moon."\n<Samurai Spirit>

"This blade is a shadow-cast by the swordsmith
Munenori, a consecrated sword forged with pure
prayers. It is the treasured heirloom of my
family. Please, use this sword to save my
daughter."\n<Samurai Spirit>\F[4]\AA[N]

"My name is Tsukimori Kageno. A foolish samurai
who failed to protect his people and child, and in
the end, fled into death, housing his soul within
this wakizashi. O white deity, please save that
child. Save Sakuya--"\n<Samurai Spirit>\F[5]\AA[N]

"The person from before. He was Sakuya's...father.
He's been waiting all this time while warding off
the curse, waiting for someone to come and save
Sakuya."\n<Yukine>\F[4]
"Yes, I will definitely fulfill your wish."\n<Yukine>\F[4]
